thread.title: Mr Kevin Young
thread.title_full: InnerTubeShop.com reviewed by Mr Kevin Young

author: Mr Kevin Young
title: Mr Kevin Young
text: Riding regularly throughout the year I go through a reasonable amount of inner tubes. The tubes supplied by Inner Tube Shop don't pretend to compete with the top of the range tubes. However they are hard wearing, a great price and the delivery is quick and on time.
